info: Rating, 5 stars,  · May 2024,  · Stayed one night
rating_comment: Recommended for everyone who wants to stay a night in Dhaka. A great apartment!

Place was probably not used in a while, bad smells were very prominent at the beginning when got inside. However the smell went off after few hours and the exhaust fan was broken identified by the management. The fan didn’t come back during our whole stay and the washroom had that hole unblocked. We had to use it some makeshift card board to cover that up. But essentially mosquitoes got inroads through the whole. So it was a pleasant stay with the place.
Very nice and clean apartment. Pretty much central location. Good for kids. I would recommend anyone with kids to try out the place.
